@penguinol 
You can see subscription message because `timeout` is set to 5, and if in 5 seconds there are no messages published, the `TimeoutError` error will be raised, connection will be reconnected and then the topic will be subscribe again. 
You can add judgement on message `type` field to avoid this problem, or you can add `timeout` in upper layer.

