```
/*

Run as follows (tested on Ubuntu 16.04, using mono):

source $DEEPCLDIR/dist/bin/activate.sh
deepcl_train datadir=/norep/data/mnist/ numtrain=1280 numtest=1280
# this will create weights.dat
